  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK785">
<l>puṇarcci paḻakutal vēṇṭā vuṇarccitā</l>
<l>ṉaṭpāṅ kiḻamai tarum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Living together and holding frequent intercourse are not necessary (for friendship) (mutual) understanding can alone create a claim for it.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
